{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A thousand years after a cataclysm shattered the world, humanity claws its way out of the underground sanctums. The surface is a vast, unforgiving frontier\u2014ripe with secrets, resources, and danger. In this bold RTS, command persistent fleets to explore sprawling environments, excavate relics of a lost age, and harvest what\u2019s left to rebuild. Research forgotten tech, construct towering strongholds, and forge unstoppable armadas. Take the helm of your ships for precision strikes or issue sweeping orders to dominate the battlefield. The last of us survived the dark\u2014now, it\u2019s time to conquer the light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552260/extras/CapitalUnit.png?t=1740778351\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage Large persistent fleets across missions. As you escort your convoy of survivors, you'll encounter new challenges, and new units to solve those challenges.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552260/extras/ENVIRONMENTWEATHER.png?t=1740778351\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try to survive an environment as hostile as the enemy</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552260/extras/EXPLOREEXCA.png?t=1740778351\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world is ripe with resources, how easily they are accessed is a different question. From the smallest collector, to the largest Heavy Excavator, each resource has its weak point.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3552260/extras/RESEARCH.png?t=1